From 823fdf18205ef1f9ec25ed2507909ef4d9ea923d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Juniper Bevensee <juniperbevensee@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Sat, 23 May 2026 12:48:21 +1200
Subject: [PATCH 18/27] feat(mattermost): observe unmentioned channel messages
 as passive context

Instead of dropping channel messages without @mention, set
observe_only=True for transcript storage. Gated by
MATTERMOST_OBSERVE_UNMENTIONED env var (default: true). Updates
existing tests and adds comprehensive test_observe_only.py suite.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
